    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "oh okay good to know. i a bit worried though because the discharge is kind of thick and yellowish in the morning and my eyelid feels a bit swollen too. it's not super painful, just uncomfortable. do u think i should bother going to the clinic for that or can i just keep using the drops and maybe try some warm compresses at home instead?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
