    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "ugh i really dont want to go a clinic right now, it's so expensive and i have so much work to catch up on. i have some leftover antibiotic eye drops from a few years ago when i had something similar. wouldn't it be faster and easier to just use those for a couple of days to see if it clears up? it's probably fine since they're the same kind of thing, right?",
